title: Nick Jonas refuses to answer questions about Kate Hudson
text:
Nick Jonas was spotted with Kate Hudson over the week but he is not willing to answer questions about their relationship just yet.
READ: Nick Jonas, Kate Hudson spark off dating rumours in Florida
Listen to Nick Jonas on Gaana.com
The Levels singer, 23, shied away from answering a question about the actress, 36, during an interview backstage at the Fillmore Silver Spring in Silver Spring, Maryland, reported People magazine.
When the interviewer asked him about Hudson, Jonas replied, "I'm not gonna get mad at you, but I'm also not gonna talk about it... I keep some things to myself."
Jonas was spotted with Hudson at Disney in Orlando last weekend, leading to speculation about a romance.
